{"tid":2175024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"議辦外持刀毀文宣揚言「淋漒水」 七旬老翁認罪判監13星期","createTime":"2020-08-26T09:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T09:03:09.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"66c7ad48197d848f7e1049970408196a199d10a6","tid":2175024,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"被告：貼我啲相，話我係藍絲<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告於今年6月5日用黑筆塗污張貼在天水圍某議員辦事處的文宣；並於同月15日，手持透明液體玻璃樽到辦事處，向女子X威嚇稱會「淋漒水」使對方人身遭受損害。翌日，被告再次毀壞議辦外15張海報，並威嚇男子Y稱「信唔信我真係用刀桶你」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/GZE5VSXC2NEOTI5QUPT5GTME2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FGZE5VSXC2NEOTI5QUPT5GTME2Y%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatpzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=b9b503ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FGZE5VSXC2NEOTI5QUPT5GTME2Y%2F&h=8de9be65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/GZE5VSXC2NEOTI5QUPT5GTME2Y/</a>"},{"pid":"93107ea06eecef256340f3d39bd71b911f4d3efe","tid":2175024,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}